window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Desperate times, desperate magic.</p> <p>I finally have the Book of Shadows. The pages call to me, begging me to devour their hidden power. There are more than just spells inside, and there are things only the High Priestess can see. </p> <p>And now I know everything I wasn’t supposed to.</p> <p>My Coven likes to keep secrets...well they’re about to get a taste of their own medicine. Rescuing Henley from the demon’s possession won’t mean a thing if we can’t close the Gap in Salem. Samhain is our deadline, and it’s right around the corner.</p> <p>The question is...can I dig deep into the world’s ancient secrets without losing myself? I don’t know, but I’m about to find out.</p> <p>The magic continues in <i>The Broken Witch</i>, the fourth book in the adventure-filled Elemental Magic series that's leaving rlisteners begging for more!</p> <p>Buy <i>The Broken Witch</i> and unlock the magic today!</p>"; 
